breath in and out (each duration one sec) continously and rapidly (beginners can start from 1 or 2 or 3 minutes and progress it till 5 minutes)
--anulom vilom pranayama:
open your thumb finger (preferably of your right hand) out and fold index finder next to it, close right nostril and breathe in through left nostril(preferable time duration-5 sec),close the left nostril through ring finger and open the right nostril and breath out through it and breath in again and repeat the process,beginners can start this with 3-5 minutes duration.
